i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iAnd the actual operand of the OR operation is 0x0000ff00 and 0x8f，		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iresulting in 0x0000ff8f.		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iOn the other hand, such phenomenon will not occur with uint16_t's:		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
